# Lab Notes

## Summary

This project was created to practice common help desk troubleshooting scenarios in a Windows environment.

## What Worked

- Task Manager performance checks
- Startup program review
- Network diagnostics commands
- Account management tasks
- Printer queue and service review

## Problems I Had

- Initial VM setup and performance tuning
- Creating realistic support scenarios
- Organizing screenshots and documentation

## What I Learned

This project helped me get more comfortable using standard Windows support tools and following a structured troubleshooting process.

## Next Time

I would like to add more advanced tickets such as VPN issues, Outlook problems, software installs, and remote support scenarios.
